title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Add a table to the report that includes a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
